short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Bridge connection between Dentinnov and X-Ray application

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
The "Dentinnov X-Ray Bridge" is a powerful Chrome extension designed to streamline the workflow of dental professionals by seamlessly integrating patient data from the Dentinnov app with popular 3D scanners such as "3Shape Unite" and X-ray native software such as "Acteon - Sopro Imaging" and "Vatech - EzDent-i".
This extension serves as a bridge between the Dentinnov app and the X-ray software, enabling dental practitioners to effortlessly access and view patient X-rays within their preferred imaging software. By eliminating the need for manual data transfer or switching between different applications, the Dentinnov X-Ray Bridge significantly enhances efficiency and productivity in the dental clinic. 
When using the Dentinnov X-Ray Bridge, dental practitioners can simply select a patient's record within the Dentinnov app. With a single click, the extension automatically opens the corresponding X-ray native software and retrieves the patient's X-ray images, eliminating the need for navigating through multiple systems.
